3
00:00:15.891 --> 00:00:18.519
{\an8}<font color="#fecb00">Lieutenant Shaw reporting as ordered. sir.</font>

4
00:00:22.981 --> 00:00:24.233
{\an8}<font color="#fecb00">At ease.</font>

5
00:00:29.112 --> 00:00:31.031
{\an8}<font color="#fecb00">I believe that's gonna stick around awhile.</font>

6
00:00:32.991 --> 00:00:36.286
<font color="#fecb00">You know. this island is lousy
with sailors. Marines.</font>

7
00:00:37.079 --> 00:00:39.799
<font color="#fecb00">You couldn't pick a fight with one of them
instead of two of our own?</font>

8
00:00:42.543 --> 00:00:45.253
{\an8}<font color="#fecb00">Sometimes the fight picks you. sir.</font>

9
00:00:45.254 --> 00:00:46.797
{\an8}<font color="#fecb00">What was the fight even about?</font>

10
00:00:50.592 --> 00:00:52.678
{\an8}<font color="#fecb00">I guess I just can't abide bullies. sir.</font>

11
00:00:53.345 --> 00:00:55.430
{\an8}<font color="#fecb00">You know. your father
threw a few punches in his day.</font>

12
00:00:56.765 --> 00:00:57.766
<font color="#fecb00">Some of them at me.</font>

13
00:00:59.142 --> 00:01:01.019
{\an8}<font color="#fecb00">What do you think he'd make of you now?</font>

14
00:01:03.480 --> 00:01:04.480
<font color="#fecb00"><i>I don't know. sir.</i></font>

15
00:01:05.274 --> 00:01:07.276
{\an8}<font color="#fecb00">Maybe we could sober him up and ask him.</font>

16
00:01:10.529 --> 00:01:11.904
<font color="#fecb00">All right.</font>

17
00:01:11.905 --> 00:01:13.991
{\an8}<font color="#fecb00">Well. some orders have come through.</font>

18
00:01:14.575 --> 00:01:17.536
<font color="#fecb00">Security escort for a Japanese scientist.</font>

19
00:01:18.161 --> 00:01:20.121
<font color="#fecb00">Sorry. sir. A Japanese scientist?</font>

20
00:01:20.122 --> 00:01:21.747
<font color="#fecb00">This isn't a milk run. Lieutenant.</font>

21
00:01:21.748 --> 00:01:25.042
<font color="#fecb00">We already lost a man
on one of these escort missions</font>

22
00:01:25.043 --> 00:01:26.170
<font color="#fecb00">a couple of months back.</font>

23
00:01:27.671 --> 00:01:31.174
{\an8}<font color="#fecb00">You will protect. observe. and report
when and if able. Understood?</font>

24
00:01:31.175 --> 00:01:32.425
{\an8}<font color="#fecb00">Understood. sir.</font>

25
00:01:32.426 --> 00:01:34.636
<font color="#fecb00">Then that is all. Lieutenant.</font>

26
00:01:36.930 --> 00:01:37.931
{\an8}<font color="#fecb00">Dismissed.</font>

27
00:01:51.278 --> 00:01:55.324
<font color="#fecb00">Excuse me. sir. you don't happen to be
Dr. Miura. would--</font>

28
00:01:57.826 --> 00:01:58.826
<font color="#fecb00">Miura?</font>

29
00:02:00.287 --> 00:02:01.288
<font color="#fecb00">Sorry.</font>

30
00:02:02.122 --> 00:02:03.290
<font color="#fecb00">I think you're here for me.</font>

31
00:02:06.543 --> 00:02:08.961
<font color="#fecb00">Wish I could say I was.
but I'm here on army business.</font>

32
00:02:09.463 --> 00:02:11.507
<font color="#fecb00">Maybe we can get a drink
on my way out. huh?</font>

33
00:02:13.133 --> 00:02:14.134
<font color="#fecb00">Wait a minute.</font>

34
00:02:15.010 --> 00:02:17.220
<font color="#fecb00">They told me they were sending
a military escort.</font>

35
00:02:17.221 --> 00:02:19.389
<font color="#fecb00">and you're the only one here in uniform.</font>

36
00:02:24.061 --> 00:02:25.853
<font color="#fecb00">I'm supposed to meet a Dr. Miura.</font>

37
00:02:25.854 --> 00:02:27.104
<font color="#fecb00">I'm Keiko Miura.</font>

38
00:02:27.105 --> 00:02:30.233
<font color="#fecb00">- You're-- Keiko. nice to meet you.
- Nice to meet you.</font>

39
00:02:30.234 --> 00:02:31.318
<font color="#fecb00">You must be his daughter?</font>

40
00:02:33.320 --> 00:02:34.445
<font color="#fecb00">Or--</font>

41
00:02:34.446 --> 00:02:38.199
<font color="#fecb00">I'm sorry. I think there's
a little miscommunication happening here.</font>

42
00:02:38.200 --> 00:02:39.825
<font color="#fecb00">- Let's start over.
- Yes. why don't we?</font>

43
00:02:39.826 --> 00:02:41.202
<font color="#fecb00">- Okay.
- You are...</font>

44
00:02:41.203 --> 00:02:44.665
<font color="#fecb00">I am Lieutenant Leland Lafayette Shaw III.
but you can call me Lee.</font>

45
00:02:46.250 --> 00:02:49.503
<font color="#fecb00">I'm Keiko Miura.
and you may call me Dr. Miura.</font>

46
00:02:59.805 --> 00:03:02.140
<font color="#fecb00">You know. these things
aren't supposed to go that fast.</font>

47
00:03:05.602 --> 00:03:06.811
<font color="#fecb00">Would you like me to drive?</font>

48
00:03:06.812 --> 00:03:07.896
<font color="#fecb00">Why?</font>

49
00:03:08.730 --> 00:03:10.148
<font color="#fecb00">Am I making you nervous?</font>

50
00:03:11.191 --> 00:03:12.651
<font color="#fecb00">Nope. But...</font>

51
00:03:14.111 --> 00:03:16.279
<font color="#fecb00">I've been assigned to you
as your military escort.</font>

52
00:03:16.280 --> 00:03:19.907
<font color="#fecb00">This is an army jeep
and I'm. you know. the army.</font>

53
00:03:19.908 --> 00:03:22.076
<font color="#fecb00">I've been driving up and down these roads
for weeks.</font>

54
00:03:22.077 --> 00:03:23.161
<font color="#fecb00">I know the way.</font>

55
00:03:25.747 --> 00:03:26.789
<font color="#fecb00">Okay then.</font>

56
00:03:26.790 --> 00:03:29.510
<font color="#fecb00">I'm starting to get the feeling
you don't really want me around here.</font>

57
00:03:31.420 --> 00:03:33.421
<font color="#fecb00">Aren't you even curious why you're here?</font>

58
00:03:33.422 --> 00:03:34.506
<font color="#fecb00">Very much so.</font>

59
00:03:37.092 --> 00:03:39.302
<font color="#fecb00">A WB-29 on a routine weather mission</font>

60
00:03:39.303 --> 00:03:42.306
<font color="#fecb00">scooped up some airborne radioisotopes
over the Philippine Sea.</font>

61
00:03:43.307 --> 00:03:47.101
<font color="#fecb00">That's pretty far south
for a Russian bomb test. They don't--</font>

62
00:03:47.102 --> 00:03:49.062
<font color="#fecb00">That's because it's not the Russians.</font>

63
00:03:50.606 --> 00:03:54.192
<font color="#fecb00">Well. it's not us. So. who is it?</font>

64
00:03:54.193 --> 00:03:56.569
<font color="#fecb00">Well. they were the wrong isotopes
for bomb fallout.</font>

65
00:03:56.570 --> 00:04:00.615
<font color="#fecb00">And meteorological data
shows they likely originated here.</font>

66
00:04:00.616 --> 00:04:01.700
<font color="#fecb00">The Philippines?</font>

67
00:04:02.534 --> 00:04:03.574
<font color="#fecb00">That's gotta be a mistake.</font>

68
00:04:04.661 --> 00:04:05.996
<font color="#fecb00">That's what I'm here to find out.</font>

69
00:04:07.623 --> 00:04:08.623
<font color="#fecb00">Okay.</font>

70
00:04:09.041 --> 00:04:12.002
<font color="#fecb00">We should get to work. Hit the gas. Doc.</font>

71
00:09:18.475 --> 00:09:19.977
<font color="#fecb00">Every day the reading diminishes.</font>

72
00:09:20.519 --> 00:09:23.104
<font color="#fecb00">Soon it'll be entirely gone.
and the trail will be lost.</font>

73
00:09:23.105 --> 00:09:25.107
<font color="#fecb00">Uh-huh. Got that. Double-time.</font>

74
00:09:25.816 --> 00:09:27.150
<font color="#fecb00">Your English is very good.</font>

75
00:09:29.236 --> 00:09:31.947
<font color="#fecb00">It came in handy when I did
my postgraduate work at Berkeley.</font>

76
00:09:34.533 --> 00:09:35.576
<font color="#fecb00">It's impressive.</font>

77
00:09:36.201 --> 00:09:38.995
<font color="#fecb00">But doesn't that make you
a little overqualified</font>

78
00:09:38.996 --> 00:09:40.162
<font color="#fecb00">for this snipe hunt?</font>

79
00:09:40.163 --> 00:09:41.664
<font color="#fecb00">This what?</font>

80
00:09:41.665 --> 00:09:43.292
<font color="#fecb00">Wild-goose chase.</font>

81
00:09:45.711 --> 00:09:48.296
<font color="#fecb00">Come on. Doc. Don't you think
if those readings were legit.</font>

82
00:09:48.297 --> 00:09:50.506
<font color="#fecb00">Washington would've sent
half the eggheads at Los Alamos</font>

83
00:09:50.507 --> 00:09:51.507
<font color="#fecb00">to check it out?</font>

84
00:09:52.009 --> 00:09:54.594
<font color="#fecb00">Not a woman.
Certainly not a Japanese woman.</font>

85
00:09:54.595 --> 00:09:56.013
<font color="#fecb00">You got that right. Yeah.</font>

86
00:09:58.932 --> 00:10:01.435
<font color="#fecb00">You want me to lie
and pretend that's not the way things are?</font>

87
00:10:03.812 --> 00:10:05.813
<font color="#fecb00">You're telling me
you didn't take one look at me</font>

88
00:10:05.814 --> 00:10:08.525
<font color="#fecb00">and make a snap judgment
about who I am the second we met?</font>

89
00:10:12.237 --> 00:10:15.741
<font color="#fecb00">It's not the same.
Leland Lafayette Shaw III.</font>

90
00:10:17.743 --> 00:10:18.911
<font color="#fecb00">Suppose it's not.</font>

91
00:10:41.725 --> 00:10:42.726
<font color="#fecb00">Do you hear that?</font>

92
00:10:50.025 --> 00:10:51.026
<font color="#fecb00">Lieutenant?</font>

93
00:10:58.367 --> 00:10:59.367
<font color="#fecb00">Lieutenant?</font>

94
00:11:12.631 --> 00:11:13.632
<font color="#fecb00">Hey.</font>

95
00:11:15.384 --> 00:11:16.592
<font color="#fecb00">Hey.</font>

96
00:11:16.593 --> 00:11:17.927
<font color="#fecb00">Don't move.</font>

97
00:11:17.928 --> 00:11:18.846
<font color="#fecb00">Lieutenant.</font>

98
00:11:18.847 --> 00:11:20.346
<font color="#fecb00">- Who are you? Who are you?
- Don't shoot.</font>

99
00:11:20.347 --> 00:11:22.515
<font color="#fecb00">I'm American. Navy vet.</font>

100
00:11:22.516 --> 00:11:25.561
<font color="#fecb00">And what are you doing here.
American Navy vet. huh? You filming us?</font>

101
00:11:26.687 --> 00:11:28.145
<font color="#fecb00">Why? You guys doing something film worthy?</font>

102
00:11:28.146 --> 00:11:30.439
<font color="#fecb00">- I asked you a question.
- I'm just asking a question back.</font>

103
00:11:30.440 --> 00:11:31.691
<font color="#fecb00">Well. I got the gun. swab.</font>

104
00:11:31.692 --> 00:11:33.192
<font color="#fecb00">so who are you
and what are you doing here?</font>

105
00:11:33.193 --> 00:11:35.195
<font color="#fecb00">- Lieutenant.
- My name's William Randa.</font>

106
00:11:36.780 --> 00:11:39.741
<font color="#fecb00">Okay. Lieutenant Shaw?</font>

107
00:11:41.451 --> 00:11:45.414
<font color="#fecb00">Look. I promise I won't shoot you
if you don't shoot me.</font>

108
00:11:46.081 --> 00:11:47.082
<font color="#fecb00">Deal?</font>

109
00:11:55.424 --> 00:11:56.424
<font color="#fecb00">All right.</font>

110
00:11:56.425 --> 00:11:57.509
<font color="#fecb00">All right?</font>

111
00:11:58.719 --> 00:12:01.079
<font color="#fecb00">Still haven't answered my question.
What are you doing here?</font>

112
00:12:02.264 --> 00:12:07.185
<font color="#fecb00">Well. you could say
I'm on a hunting expedition.</font>

113
00:12:07.186 --> 00:12:09.020
<font color="#fecb00">I'm a cryptozoologist.</font>

114
00:12:09.021 --> 00:12:12.983
<font color="#fecb00">- You're a cryptozoo-- What?
- He studies animals that don't exist.</font>

115
00:12:13.567 --> 00:12:14.568
<font color="#fecb00">Yeah.</font>

116
00:12:16.445 --> 00:12:18.739
<font color="#fecb00">Atmospheric sampler? Spectrometer?</font>

117
00:12:19.323 --> 00:12:21.157
<font color="#fecb00">- Hey. is this a radiation monitor here?
- Hey.</font>

118
00:12:21.158 --> 00:12:22.575
<font color="#fecb00">- Easy.
- Don't touch that.</font>

119
00:12:22.576 --> 00:12:24.411
<font color="#fecb00">Sorry. I just--
I've never seen one before.</font>

120
00:12:26.038 --> 00:12:27.413
<font color="#fecb00">Just wanted to check it out.</font>

121
00:12:27.414 --> 00:12:30.709
<font color="#fecb00">'Cause it seems like maybe
we're out here hunting for the same thing.</font>

122
00:12:32.085 --> 00:12:33.879
<font color="#fecb00">And what's that. Mr. Randa?</font>

123
00:12:35.255 --> 00:12:36.381
<font color="#fecb00">The truth.</font>

124
00:13:18.048 --> 00:13:19.674
<font color="#fecb00"><i>Catey. where have you been?</i></font>

125
00:13:19.675 --> 00:13:20.675
<font color="#fecb00">I'm sorry. I--</font>

126
00:13:20.676 --> 00:13:22.260
<font color="#fecb00"><i>I've been calling and calling you.</i></font>

127
00:13:22.261 --> 00:13:24.053
<font color="#fecb00">Mom. I'm fine. I'm coming home.</font>

128
00:13:24.054 --> 00:13:26.806
<font color="#fecb00"><i>Already? What did you find out?</i></font>

129
00:13:26.807 --> 00:13:28.516
<font color="#fecb00">It doesn't have anything to do with us.</font>

130
00:13:28.517 --> 00:13:30.768
<font color="#fecb00"><i>What does that mean?
What does it have to do--</i></font>

131
00:13:30.769 --> 00:13:32.646
<font color="#fecb00">What did it always have to do with. Mom?
Him.</font>

132
00:13:33.188 --> 00:13:34.230
<font color="#fecb00"><i>Catey.</i></font>

133
00:13:34.231 --> 00:13:36.232
<font color="#fecb00">- We'll talk when I get home. okay?
- Don't do this.</font>

134
00:13:36.233 --> 00:13:37.734
<font color="#fecb00">- Love you. Bye.
- Catey. do not--</font>

135
00:13:44.616 --> 00:13:45.617
<font color="#fecb00">American?</font>

136
00:13:47.536 --> 00:13:48.744
<font color="#fecb00">Excuse me?</font>

137
00:13:48.745 --> 00:13:50.663
<font color="#fecb00">Sorry. I didn't mean to eavesdrop.
I just--</font>

138
00:13:50.664 --> 00:13:52.165
<font color="#fecb00">I overheard your accent.</font>

139
00:13:53.208 --> 00:13:56.544
<font color="#fecb00">Sometimes this place can make you feel
like you're stranded on another planet.</font>

140
00:13:56.545 --> 00:13:57.629
<font color="#fecb00">Glad I could help.</font>

141
00:14:05.429 --> 00:14:07.305
<font color="#fecb00">- Where are you heading?
- Look. I don't mean to be rude.</font>

142
00:14:07.306 --> 00:14:10.308
<font color="#fecb00">but I've made all the new friends
I can handle for one day. thanks.</font>

143
00:14:10.309 --> 00:14:12.185
<font color="#fecb00">Yeah. Nah. nah. Hey. I totally get it.</font>

144
00:14:12.186 --> 00:14:16.480
<font color="#fecb00">This young woman abroad
runs into a strange man</font>

145
00:14:16.481 --> 00:14:17.566
<font color="#fecb00">at the train station.</font>

146
00:14:18.567 --> 00:14:21.445
<font color="#fecb00">And next thing you know.
you're buried alive in a coffin somewhere.</font>

147
00:14:23.989 --> 00:14:25.824
<font color="#fecb00">I can't imagine that that helped.</font>

148
00:14:26.992 --> 00:14:29.620
<font color="#fecb00">Hey. Wait. Look. Hey. I'm harmless.</font>

149
00:14:30.495 --> 00:14:31.495
<font color="#fecb00">My name's Tim.</font>

150
00:14:32.456 --> 00:14:34.498
<font color="#fecb00">They don't come much more harmless
than the "Tim" variety.</font>

151
00:14:34.499 --> 00:14:35.584
<font color="#fecb00">Have a nice night. Tim.</font>

152
00:14:37.085 --> 00:14:38.629
<font color="#fecb00">I need to talk to you about the files.</font>

153
00:14:40.714 --> 00:14:41.715
<font color="#fecb00">I don't--</font>

154
00:14:43.425 --> 00:14:44.425
<font color="#fecb00">What files?</font>

155
00:14:44.426 --> 00:14:46.178
<font color="#fecb00">I work for Monarch.</font>

156
00:14:49.014 --> 00:14:50.098
<font color="#fecb00">You're not in trouble.</font>

157
00:14:50.891 --> 00:14:52.391
<font color="#fecb00">Not yet.</font>

158
00:14:52.392 --> 00:14:54.645
<font color="#fecb00">Those files belong to us.</font>

159
00:14:55.604 --> 00:14:58.106
<font color="#fecb00">and they are more important
than you could possibly imagine.</font>

160
00:15:01.944 --> 00:15:03.111
<font color="#fecb00">I need to make a call.</font>

161
00:15:04.821 --> 00:15:07.241
<font color="#fecb00">Okay. Let's make a call.</font>

162
00:15:25.175 --> 00:15:26.426
<font color="#fecb00">All right. All right.</font>

163
00:15:27.261 --> 00:15:28.512
<font color="#fecb00">Make your call.</font>

164
00:15:30.264 --> 00:15:31.265
<font color="#fecb00">Speaker. please.</font>

165
00:15:32.766 --> 00:15:33.851
<font color="#fecb00">Sure.</font>

166
00:15:35.310 --> 00:15:37.771
<font color="#fecb00"><i>Cate? Hello? Cate?</i></font>

167
00:15:43.735 --> 00:15:44.987
<font color="#fecb00">No.</font>

168
00:15:45.821 --> 00:15:46.905
<font color="#fecb00">No.</font>

169
00:15:50.617 --> 00:15:52.493
<font color="#fecb00">I said you weren't in trouble.</font>

170
00:15:52.494 --> 00:15:54.371
<font color="#fecb00">"Yet". You said "yet."</font>

171
00:16:03.839 --> 00:16:05.798
<font color="#fecb00">Look. I swear we're not gonna hurt you.</font>

172
00:16:05.799 --> 00:16:06.966
<font color="#fecb00">No. you can't do this.</font>

173
00:16:06.967 --> 00:16:09.427
<font color="#fecb00">- I can't let you see where we're going.
- No! You don't understand.</font>

174
00:16:09.428 --> 00:16:11.263
<font color="#fecb00">I can't breathe. I can't--</font>

175
00:16:14.016 --> 00:16:14.892
<font color="#fecb00">I can't--</font>

176
00:16:14.893 --> 00:16:17.811
<font color="#fecb00">Relax. You're gonna be fine.
Just breathe. okay?</font>

177
00:16:18.520 --> 00:16:20.855
<font color="#fecb00">- Let me out. Let me out!
- Calm down. Relax.</font>

178
00:16:20.856 --> 00:16:23.650
<font color="#fecb00">- Let me out!
- Relax. Calm down.</font>

179
00:16:25.444 --> 00:16:26.528
<font color="#fecb00">Hey!</font>

180
00:16:27.446 --> 00:16:29.488
<font color="#fecb00">Get her under control. man.</font>

181
00:16:29.489 --> 00:16:30.532
<font color="#fecb00">Let me out!</font>

182
00:17:27.881 --> 00:17:28.881
<font color="#fecb00">What?</font>

183
00:17:29.466 --> 00:17:30.843
<font color="#fecb00">Why aren't you answering my texts?</font>

184
00:17:31.343 --> 00:17:33.554
<font color="#fecb00">When's the last time
I answered one of your texts?</font>

185
00:17:34.221 --> 00:17:36.138
<font color="#fecb00">I don't know... I thought...</font>

186
00:17:36.139 --> 00:17:37.223
<font color="#fecb00">You thought?</font>

187
00:17:37.224 --> 00:17:39.475
<font color="#fecb00">You thought that
because of your crazy family drama</font>

188
00:17:39.476 --> 00:17:42.354
<font color="#fecb00">that what happened between us
is ancient history?</font>

189
00:17:44.439 --> 00:17:46.024
<font color="#fecb00">What do you want from me?</font>

190
00:17:50.070 --> 00:17:52.364
<font color="#fecb00">I found this in my father's office.</font>

191
00:17:53.699 --> 00:17:55.576
<font color="#fecb00">I do audio. not home movies.</font>

192
00:17:58.453 --> 00:18:00.080
<font color="#fecb00">I told you I was sorry.</font>

193
00:18:01.081 --> 00:18:02.291
<font color="#fecb00">Apology accepted.</font>

194
00:18:03.166 --> 00:18:04.166
<font color="#fecb00">I'm sorry too.</font>

195
00:18:05.085 --> 00:18:08.254
<font color="#fecb00">I grabbed onto you
to keep my head above water.</font>

196
00:18:08.255 --> 00:18:09.882
<font color="#fecb00">and you didn't wanna drown. I get it.</font>

197
00:18:15.053 --> 00:18:16.054
<font color="#fecb00">You should go home now.</font>

198
00:18:16.638 --> 00:18:17.930
<font color="#fecb00">Wait. wait. wait.</font>

199
00:18:17.931 --> 00:18:20.516
<font color="#fecb00">I want those old computer files we found.</font>

200
00:18:20.517 --> 00:18:21.684
<font color="#fecb00">Why?</font>

201
00:18:21.685 --> 00:18:24.812
<font color="#fecb00">Because they're mine.
What difference does it make to you?</font>

202
00:18:24.813 --> 00:18:26.064
<font color="#fecb00">I'm busy.</font>

203
00:18:26.857 --> 00:18:27.983
<font color="#fecb00">Come back tomorrow.</font>

204
00:19:04.728 --> 00:19:06.522
<font color="#fecb00">She sounded French.</font>

205
00:19:07.439 --> 00:19:10.066
<font color="#fecb00">You said they were American.</font>

206
00:19:10.067 --> 00:19:11.151
<font color="#fecb00">The man was.</font>

207
00:19:13.195 --> 00:19:14.196
<font color="#fecb00">Tim?</font>

208
00:19:15.697 --> 00:19:17.866
<font color="#fecb00">Do you have some identification?</font>

209
00:19:22.079 --> 00:19:24.414
<font color="#fecb00">I lost my bag when I ran away.</font>

210
00:19:25.791 --> 00:19:26.791
<font color="#fecb00">My passport...</font>

211
00:19:27.292 --> 00:19:28.710
<font color="#fecb00">...my phone. all my money.</font>

212
00:19:30.254 --> 00:19:32.548
<font color="#fecb00">And you're sure this wasn't some kind of...</font>

213
00:19:32.840 --> 00:19:34.716
<font color="#fecb00">...misunderstanding?</font>

214
00:19:36.301 --> 00:19:37.301
<font color="#fecb00">What?</font>

215
00:19:38.136 --> 00:19:41.640
<font color="#fecb00">Tourists come here to enjoy
what Tokyo has to offer.</font>

216
00:19:42.975 --> 00:19:45.227
<font color="#fecb00">The nightlife. Some karaoke.</font>

217
00:19:45.686 --> 00:19:46.728
<font color="#fecb00">But...</font>

218
00:19:46.979 --> 00:19:48.397
<font color="#fecb00">...it's easy to overindulge.</font>

219
00:19:49.565 --> 00:19:51.441
<font color="#fecb00">You think I'm drunk?</font>

220
00:19:53.068 --> 00:19:55.279
<font color="#fecb00">I was almost kidnapped!</font>

221
00:20:01.368 --> 00:20:03.912
<font color="#fecb00">If you feel you are in danger...</font>

222
00:20:05.080 --> 00:20:08.208
<font color="#fecb00">...I would recommend you contact the
American Embassy.</font>

223
00:20:09.626 --> 00:20:11.003
<font color="#fecb00">Wait here.</font>

224
00:20:11.461 --> 00:20:13.005
<font color="#fecb00">I will get you the address.</font>

225
00:20:42.034 --> 00:20:43.034
<font color="#fecb00">I'm home.</font>

226
00:20:43.243 --> 00:20:44.244
<font color="#fecb00">Welcome back.</font>

227
00:20:53.712 --> 00:20:54.963
<font color="#fecb00">Have you had dinner?</font>

228
00:20:55.672 --> 00:20:56.672
<font color="#fecb00">I'm not hungry.</font>

229
00:20:56.673 --> 00:20:57.591
<font color="#fecb00">You haven't?</font>

230
00:20:57.592 --> 00:20:59.134
<font color="#fecb00">I was going to warm up the curry.</font>

231
00:21:00.511 --> 00:21:01.511
<font color="#fecb00">What's this?</font>

232
00:21:02.387 --> 00:21:05.098
<font color="#fecb00">His life was not easy. you know.</font>

233
00:21:05.807 --> 00:21:08.769
<font color="#fecb00">He lost so much when he was young.</font>

234
00:21:11.647 --> 00:21:13.690
<font color="#fecb00">You're defending him?</font>

235
00:21:14.441 --> 00:21:15.526
<font color="#fecb00">Aren't you angry?</font>

236
00:21:16.777 --> 00:21:19.780
<font color="#fecb00">You're angry. Kentaro.</font>

237
00:21:20.822 --> 00:21:23.200
<font color="#fecb00">Do you feel better?</font>

238
00:21:34.336 --> 00:21:35.963
<font color="#fecb00">What are you doing?</font>

239
00:21:37.214 --> 00:21:38.257
<font color="#fecb00">Now I'm angry too.</font>

240
00:21:40.592 --> 00:21:41.885
<font color="#fecb00">Join me. Kentaro.</font>

241
00:21:45.639 --> 00:21:46.639
<font color="#fecb00">Seriously?!</font>

242
00:21:46.932 --> 00:21:47.933
<font color="#fecb00">Throw it!</font>

243
00:21:50.769 --> 00:21:51.603
<font color="#fecb00">More.</font>

244
00:21:51.604 --> 00:21:52.729
<font color="#fecb00">Here.</font>

245
00:22:01.196 --> 00:22:03.282
<font color="#fecb00">Now we both feel better. right?</font>

246
00:22:05.450 --> 00:22:06.827
<font color="#fecb00">A little.</font>

247
00:22:10.706 --> 00:22:12.374
<font color="#fecb00">I'll warm up the curry.</font>

248
00:22:34.938 --> 00:22:37.607
<font color="#fecb00">So. you guys are
following the radiation. aren't you?</font>

249
00:22:37.608 --> 00:22:38.733
<font color="#fecb00">And how do you know about that?</font>

250
00:22:38.734 --> 00:22:40.985
<font color="#fecb00">Well. I know you're not gonna find
what's out there</font>

251
00:22:40.986 --> 00:22:42.445
<font color="#fecb00">following a Geiger counter.</font>

252
00:22:42.446 --> 00:22:44.363
<font color="#fecb00">What should we be following.
Mr. Randa?</font>

253
00:22:44.364 --> 00:22:45.866
<font color="#fecb00">Just Billy.</font>

254
00:22:46.617 --> 00:22:49.327
<font color="#fecb00">I think you should be following
the stories. Folklore. Legends.</font>

255
00:22:49.328 --> 00:22:52.747
<font color="#fecb00">You know. the people of these mountains.
they have an oral tradition</font>

256
00:22:52.748 --> 00:22:56.335
<font color="#fecb00">about a dragon that carves a path of fire
across the sky.</font>

257
00:22:57.753 --> 00:23:00.422
<font color="#fecb00">Or maybe a path of ionizing radiation.</font>

258
00:23:01.965 --> 00:23:05.344
<font color="#fecb00">So. you're hunting dragons.</font>

259
00:23:06.887 --> 00:23:08.930
<font color="#fecb00">I told you. I'm looking for the truth.</font>

260
00:23:08.931 --> 00:23:10.932
<font color="#fecb00">That's great. But we got work to do.</font>

261
00:23:10.933 --> 00:23:12.683
<font color="#fecb00">so it's time for you to hit the trail. bud.</font>

262
00:23:12.684 --> 00:23:14.185
<font color="#fecb00">Wait a minute. Lieutenant.</font>

263
00:23:14.186 --> 00:23:16.730
<font color="#fecb00">I don't think it's such a bad idea
for Mr. Randa to join us.</font>

264
00:23:17.689 --> 00:23:18.982
<font color="#fecb00">I think it's a terrible idea.</font>

265
00:23:19.566 --> 00:23:21.526
<font color="#fecb00">You're not here
to think for me. Lieutenant.</font>

266
00:23:21.527 --> 00:23:23.986
<font color="#fecb00">Look at him. Smell him.</font>

267
00:23:23.987 --> 00:23:25.613
<font color="#fecb00">He's probably been lost out here
for weeks.</font>

268
00:23:25.614 --> 00:23:27.240
<font color="#fecb00">Hey. hey. I know exactly where I am. pal.</font>

269
00:23:27.241 --> 00:23:28.616
<font color="#fecb00">- Do you?
- Yes.</font>

270
00:23:28.617 --> 00:23:31.994
<font color="#fecb00">No. Look. I am here at the behest
of the US Army. and my orders are--</font>

271
00:23:31.995 --> 00:23:34.413
<font color="#fecb00">Your orders are to provide me
with whatever assistance I require.</font>

272
00:23:34.414 --> 00:23:38.125
<font color="#fecb00">My orders are to provide you
with operational security.</font>

273
00:23:38.126 --> 00:23:42.547
<font color="#fecb00">and I cannot do that with our new friend.
Billy the jungle hermit. hanging around.</font>

274
00:23:42.548 --> 00:23:43.632
<font color="#fecb00">Wow.</font>

275
00:23:47.052 --> 00:23:49.263
<font color="#fecb00">Fine. Just go then.</font>

276
00:23:50.472 --> 00:23:51.472
<font color="#fecb00">Don't tempt me. Doc.</font>

277
00:23:53.016 --> 00:23:54.225
<font color="#fecb00">I didn't ask for you.</font>

278
00:23:54.226 --> 00:23:57.019
<font color="#fecb00">I don't need you and I don't want you.</font>

279
00:23:57.020 --> 00:24:00.899
<font color="#fecb00">So. you are relieved of
any responsibility for me.</font>

280
00:24:02.776 --> 00:24:03.944
<font color="#fecb00">Dismissed.</font>

281
00:24:07.239 --> 00:24:08.782
<font color="#fecb00">I'll send someone back with the jeep.</font>

282
00:24:21.086 --> 00:24:22.212
<font color="#fecb00">Shall we go?</font>

283
00:24:36.393 --> 00:24:38.644
<font color="#fecb00">So. have you ever seen a dragon?</font>

284
00:24:38.645 --> 00:24:39.688
<font color="#fecb00">Once.</font>

285
00:24:40.189 --> 00:24:42.982
<font color="#fecb00">Well. maybe.
It's kind of why I started doing this.</font>

286
00:24:42.983 --> 00:24:44.734
<font color="#fecb00">Trying to prove I'm not crazy.</font>

287
00:24:44.735 --> 00:24:46.110
<font color="#fecb00">You think I'm crazy?</font>

288
00:24:46.111 --> 00:24:47.529
<font color="#fecb00">I don't even know you.</font>

289
00:24:48.030 --> 00:24:49.031
<font color="#fecb00">That's true.</font>

290
00:24:49.531 --> 00:24:51.411
<font color="#fecb00">Do you often
follow strange men into the jungle?</font>

291
00:24:52.367 --> 00:24:54.369
<font color="#fecb00">This is my second time today.</font>

292
00:24:57.122 --> 00:24:58.373
<font color="#fecb00">We call 'em MUTO's.</font>

293
00:24:59.208 --> 00:25:02.460
<font color="#fecb00">For Massive Unidentified
Terrestrial Organisms.</font>

294
00:25:02.461 --> 00:25:03.961
<font color="#fecb00">I came up with that.</font>

295
00:25:03.962 --> 00:25:07.632
<font color="#fecb00">Terrestrial.
So. you don't think they're space aliens?</font>

296
00:25:07.633 --> 00:25:09.176
<font color="#fecb00">You do think I'm crazy.</font>

297
00:25:09.843 --> 00:25:10.677
<font color="#fecb00">I'm a scientist.</font>

298
00:25:10.678 --> 00:25:12.887
<font color="#fecb00">I believe what
the evidence tells me to be true.</font>

299
00:25:12.888 --> 00:25:14.097
<font color="#fecb00">Okay.</font>

300
00:25:15.098 --> 00:25:18.100
<font color="#fecb00">Everyone around here tells
some version of the same story.</font>

301
00:25:18.101 --> 00:25:19.770
<font color="#fecb00">- Okay.
- Lights in the sky.</font>

302
00:25:21.396 --> 00:25:24.357
<font color="#fecb00">And whatever's making them
has been tracing the same path</font>

303
00:25:24.358 --> 00:25:27.985
<font color="#fecb00">over and over and over again.
going back centuries.</font>

304
00:25:27.986 --> 00:25:30.989
<font color="#fecb00">- Like comets.
- No. More like migrating birds.</font>

305
00:25:31.907 --> 00:25:32.908
<font color="#fecb00">Hold on.</font>

306
00:25:33.992 --> 00:25:35.452
<font color="#fecb00">I have to show you something.</font>

307
00:25:36.745 --> 00:25:38.663
<font color="#fecb00">These are the tracks</font>

308
00:25:38.664 --> 00:25:41.375
<font color="#fecb00">of the radiation readings
from our surveillance aircraft.</font>

309
00:25:46.755 --> 00:25:47.881
<font color="#fecb00">See this?</font>

310
00:25:55.514 --> 00:25:56.890
<font color="#fecb00">Incredible.</font>

311
00:26:00.185 --> 00:26:01.770
<font color="#fecb00">- This way. This way. Come on.
- Okay.</font>

312
00:26:02.479 --> 00:26:03.604
<font color="#fecb00">Where are we going?</font>

313
00:26:03.605 --> 00:26:05.190
<font color="#fecb00">We're following the map.</font>

314
00:26:18.036 --> 00:26:19.079
<font color="#fecb00">We're almost there.</font>

315
00:26:19.746 --> 00:26:21.290
<font color="#fecb00">Almost where?</font>

316
00:26:24.585 --> 00:26:25.669
<font color="#fecb00">What is it?</font>

317
00:26:31.258 --> 00:26:32.426
<font color="#fecb00">What is that?</font>

318
00:26:37.973 --> 00:26:38.974
<font color="#fecb00">The Lawton.</font>

319
00:27:20.182 --> 00:27:21.183
<font color="#fecb00">I don't know.</font>

320
00:27:22.267 --> 00:27:23.851
<font color="#fecb00">You wanna take a look
and see what's on these.</font>

321
00:27:23.852 --> 00:27:25.687
<font color="#fecb00">I have no idea if they're any good but...</font>

322
00:27:33.487 --> 00:27:34.488
<font color="#fecb00">You do it.</font>

323
00:27:50.963 --> 00:27:55.175
<font color="#fecb00">Hiroshi was eighteen
when his father died in Vietnam.</font>

324
00:27:59.221 --> 00:28:02.349
<font color="#fecb00">His Uncle Lee was
the only family he had left.</font>

325
00:28:03.267 --> 00:28:06.270
<font color="#fecb00">If they were so close.
why didn't Dad ever mention him?</font>

326
00:28:08.272 --> 00:28:10.023
<font color="#fecb00">I think something happened between them.</font>

327
00:28:10.983 --> 00:28:12.526
<font color="#fecb00">He didn't like to talk about</font>

328
00:28:13.277 --> 00:28:15.821
<font color="#fecb00">some parts of his life.</font>

329
00:28:17.948 --> 00:28:19.324
<font color="#fecb00">Is he still alive?</font>

330
00:28:20.909 --> 00:28:21.994
<font color="#fecb00">Oh. I don't know.</font>

331
00:28:23.495 --> 00:28:25.455
<font color="#fecb00">This would have been a long time ago.</font>

332
00:28:28.166 --> 00:28:29.293
<font color="#fecb00">Sorry.</font>

333
00:28:31.295 --> 00:28:32.713
<font color="#fecb00">"CALL ME! IT'S IMPORTANT!"</font>

334
00:28:36.675 --> 00:28:37.800
<font color="#fecb00">I'll get it.</font>

335
00:28:37.801 --> 00:28:38.844
<font color="#fecb00">Thank you.</font>

336
00:28:47.186 --> 00:28:48.186
<font color="#fecb00">Good Evening.</font>

337
00:28:48.604 --> 00:28:50.188
<font color="#fecb00">Do you speak English?</font>

338
00:28:50.189 --> 00:28:51.607
<font color="#fecb00">Yes.</font>

339
00:28:52.149 --> 00:28:53.900
<font color="#fecb00">That's great. actually.</font>

340
00:28:53.901 --> 00:28:57.069
<font color="#fecb00">That makes this much easier.
for me anyway.</font>

341
00:28:57.070 --> 00:28:58.154
<font color="#fecb00">May we come in?</font>

342
00:28:58.155 --> 00:29:01.032
<font color="#fecb00">- No. Who are you?
- It's official business.</font>

343
00:29:01.033 --> 00:29:03.826
<font color="#fecb00">We're with
a special government task force.</font>

344
00:29:03.827 --> 00:29:05.745
<font color="#fecb00">- Which government?
- You know what?</font>

345
00:29:05.746 --> 00:29:08.456
<font color="#fecb00">We'll be in and out
before you even know it.</font>

346
00:29:08.457 --> 00:29:10.918
<font color="#fecb00">Wow. You have a lovely home.</font>

347
00:29:11.710 --> 00:29:13.045
<font color="#fecb00">Who are they?</font>

348
00:29:14.630 --> 00:29:16.131
<font color="#fecb00">What do you want?</font>

349
00:29:17.591 --> 00:29:19.050
<font color="#fecb00">I want Bill Randa's files.</font>

350
00:29:19.051 --> 00:29:20.343
<font color="#fecb00">No. you need to leave.</font>

351
00:29:20.344 --> 00:29:22.762
<font color="#fecb00">No. you need to hand over those files.</font>

352
00:29:22.763 --> 00:29:25.848
<font color="#fecb00">Otherwise. you. your friends.</font>

353
00:29:25.849 --> 00:29:28.185
<font color="#fecb00">and your mother
are gonna be in a lot of trouble.</font>

354
00:29:28.560 --> 00:29:29.436
<font color="#fecb00">Kentaro...?</font>

355
00:29:29.436 --> 00:29:30.436
<font color="#fecb00">It's okay.</font>

356
00:29:30.938 --> 00:29:33.607
<font color="#fecb00">There's something that your son stole.</font>

357
00:29:35.192 --> 00:29:37.152
<font color="#fecb00">He's going to have to come with us.</font>

358
00:29:39.071 --> 00:29:40.071
<font color="#fecb00">Is it true?</font>

359
00:29:40.239 --> 00:29:42.073
<font color="#fecb00">Did you take something of theirs?</font>

360
00:29:42.074 --> 00:29:43.533
<font color="#fecb00">They say I stole some files.</font>

361
00:29:43.534 --> 00:29:44.743
<font color="#fecb00">Enough.</font>

362
00:29:44.993 --> 00:29:46.370
<font color="#fecb00">Let's have it.</font>

363
00:29:47.120 --> 00:29:52.084
<font color="#fecb00">If he returns whatever he took.
will you leave him alone?</font>

364
00:29:52.668 --> 00:29:53.668
<font color="#fecb00">Of course.</font>

365
00:29:58.507 --> 00:30:00.300
<font color="#fecb00">If you have what they are looking for...</font>

366
00:30:01.009 --> 00:30:02.469
<font color="#fecb00">...you should give it to them.</font>

367
00:30:03.136 --> 00:30:04.179
<font color="#fecb00">Are you sure?</font>

368
00:30:06.890 --> 00:30:09.560
<font color="#fecb00">It must be very important.</font>

369
00:30:15.232 --> 00:30:16.233
<font color="#fecb00">I'll get it.</font>

370
00:30:17.693 --> 00:30:19.278
<font color="#fecb00">Amazing. Thank you.</font>

371
00:30:20.529 --> 00:30:23.031
<font color="#fecb00">Tea? You like tea?</font>

372
00:30:24.032 --> 00:30:25.032
<font color="#fecb00">Tea?</font>

373
00:30:25.450 --> 00:30:26.784
<font color="#fecb00">No. We're good. Thanks.</font>

374
00:30:26.785 --> 00:30:29.204
<font color="#fecb00">I hope my son hasn't caused
any trouble for you.</font>

375
00:30:29.830 --> 00:30:31.330
<font color="#fecb00">He's a good man now.</font>

376
00:30:31.331 --> 00:30:33.959
<font color="#fecb00">but when he was younger
there were so many problems!</font>

377
00:30:34.668 --> 00:30:36.544
<font color="#fecb00">- So much drinking!
- Hurry up!</font>

378
00:30:36.545 --> 00:30:39.131
<font color="#fecb00">I wanted him to find a nice girl.</font>

379
00:30:39.840 --> 00:30:41.633
<font color="#fecb00">Someone to settle him down.</font>

380
00:30:42.217 --> 00:30:44.218
<font color="#fecb00">You are very attractive.</font>

381
00:30:44.219 --> 00:30:45.554
<font color="#fecb00">Are you single?</font>

382
00:30:49.433 --> 00:30:51.309
<font color="#fecb00">Oh. shit.</font>

383
00:30:51.310 --> 00:30:53.645
<font color="#fecb00">- Shit.
- Kentaro!</font>

384
00:30:54.730 --> 00:30:55.730
<font color="#fecb00">Open up!</font>

385
00:30:55.814 --> 00:30:57.357
<font color="#fecb00">Kentaro. run!</font>

386
00:31:46.490 --> 00:31:47.823
<font color="#fecb00">You know this ship?</font>

387
00:31:47.824 --> 00:31:49.243
<font color="#fecb00">USS Lawton.</font>

388
00:31:50.202 --> 00:31:53.455
<font color="#fecb00">Went down 200 miles west of Pearl in 1943.</font>

389
00:31:54.081 --> 00:31:55.457
<font color="#fecb00">Pearl Harbor?</font>

390
00:31:56.250 --> 00:31:58.626
<font color="#fecb00">That's 5.000 miles from here.</font>

391
00:31:58.627 --> 00:31:59.711
<font color="#fecb00">Exactly.</font>

392
00:32:17.396 --> 00:32:18.564
<font color="#fecb00">Is this safe?</font>

393
00:32:29.575 --> 00:32:30.742
<font color="#fecb00">Mr. Randa.</font>

394
00:32:31.702 --> 00:32:34.745
<font color="#fecb00">You said you study myths. stories.</font>

395
00:32:34.746 --> 00:32:37.624
<font color="#fecb00">I'm interested in why
people tell the stories they tell.</font>

396
00:32:42.421 --> 00:32:44.047
<font color="#fecb00">What inspired the storyteller.</font>

397
00:32:51.805 --> 00:32:52.806
<font color="#fecb00">What terrified 'em.</font>

398
00:33:11.366 --> 00:33:12.367
<font color="#fecb00">What is it?</font>

399
00:33:14.786 --> 00:33:17.539
<font color="#fecb00">Mr. Randa.
Maybe we should stick together--</font>

400
00:33:32.930 --> 00:33:33.931
<font color="#fecb00">Mr. Randa.</font>

401
00:33:36.767 --> 00:33:37.768
<font color="#fecb00">Billy.</font>

402
00:33:47.569 --> 00:33:49.112
<font color="#fecb00">You were on this ship.</font>

403
00:33:52.824 --> 00:33:53.825
<font color="#fecb00">Yeah.</font>

404
00:33:57.246 --> 00:33:58.956
<font color="#fecb00">Is this what you were looking for?</font>

405
00:33:59.623 --> 00:34:01.124
<font color="#fecb00">Did you know it was here?</font>

406
00:34:05.087 --> 00:34:06.088
<font color="#fecb00">Did I know?</font>

407
00:34:10.926 --> 00:34:12.135
<font color="#fecb00">Let's say hoped.</font>

408
00:34:15.138 --> 00:34:16.223
<font color="#fecb00">Not very scientific.</font>

409
00:34:19.268 --> 00:34:21.645
<font color="#fecb00">I know we hit something
in the water that night.</font>

410
00:34:22.312 --> 00:34:23.981
<font color="#fecb00">We figured it was a Japanese sub.</font>

411
00:34:27.025 --> 00:34:29.110
<font color="#fecb00">The whole ship went down
in less than three minutes.</font>

412
00:34:30.779 --> 00:34:31.864
<font color="#fecb00">Who else survived?</font>

413
00:34:36.451 --> 00:34:37.452
<font color="#fecb00">Only me.</font>

414
00:35:41.558 --> 00:35:42.767
<font color="#fecb00">Going to the back.</font>

415
00:35:42.768 --> 00:35:43.852
<font color="#fecb00">Okay.</font>

416
00:36:00.202 --> 00:36:01.912
<font color="#fecb00">Who are you? Jason Bourne?</font>

417
00:36:03.413 --> 00:36:05.624
<font color="#fecb00">You're from San Francisco.
You were there that day.</font>

418
00:36:06.208 --> 00:36:07.416
<font color="#fecb00">You don't have a bag packed.</font>

419
00:36:07.417 --> 00:36:09.752
<font color="#fecb00">ready to head for higher ground
