444
00:37:56.109 --> 00:37:57.361
<font color="#fecb00">Yeah.</font>

445
00:38:06.745 --> 00:38:07.995
<font color="#fecb00">That wasn't there before.</font>

446
00:38:07.996 --> 00:38:09.790
<font color="#fecb00">- This is fresh.
