450
00:38:15.838 --> 00:38:17.214
<font color="#fecb00">I don't know. Come on.</font>

451
00:38:37.609 --> 00:38:39.110
<font color="#fecb00">You're here to see the Colonel?</font>

452
00:38:39.111 --> 00:38:41.071
<font color="#fecb00">Yes. we are.</font>

453
00:38:41.780 --> 00:38:43.448
<font color="#fecb00">If he's still alive.</font>

454
00:38:43.824 --> 00:38:45.701
<font color="#fecb00">So. we can see the Colonel?</font>

455
00:39:07.681 --> 00:39:08.974
<font color="#fecb00">Colonel Shaw?</font>

456
00:39:22.446 --> 00:39:23.447
<font color="#fecb00">What's your name?</font>

457
00:39:24.740 --> 00:39:25.741
<font color="#fecb00">Kentaro.</font>

458
00:39:26.241 --> 00:39:27.283
<font color="#fecb00">Kentaro what?</font>

459
00:39:27.284 --> 00:39:28.368
<font color="#fecb00">Randa.</font>

460
00:39:30.537 --> 00:39:34.583
<font color="#fecb00">Oh. my God. You're Hiroshi's boy.</font>

461
00:39:36.418 --> 00:39:37.919
<font color="#fecb00">And you?</font>

462
00:39:37.920 --> 00:39:40.464
<font color="#fecb00">I'm Cate Randa.</font>

463
00:39:41.173 --> 00:39:42.257
<font color="#fecb00">Course you are.</font>

464
00:39:45.344 --> 00:39:48.429
<font color="#fecb00">I didn't know Hiroshi even had a daughter.</font>

465
00:39:48.430 --> 00:39:50.598
<font color="#fecb00">Well. I didn't know he had a son.</font>

466
00:39:50.599 --> 00:39:53.227
<font color="#fecb00">Turns out he was good at keeping secrets.</font>

467
00:39:57.523 --> 00:39:59.191
<font color="#fecb00">Not my drama. No relation.</font>

468
00:40:00.108 --> 00:40:02.319
<font color="#fecb00">- We wanted to ask you about our fa--
- Why don't we...</font>

469
00:40:05.239 --> 00:40:06.240
<font color="#fecb00">Yeah. Come on.</font>

470
00:40:07.449 --> 00:40:08.450
<font color="#fecb00">Let's get some air.</font>

471
00:40:09.451 --> 00:40:10.577
<font color="#fecb00">Come on.</font>

472
00:40:15.666 --> 00:40:19.001
<font color="#fecb00">If you guys could just kinda keep
your voices down. that'd be good.</font>

473
00:40:19.002 --> 00:40:20.587
<font color="#fecb00">Tell me. how'd you get here?</font>

474
00:40:21.421 --> 00:40:22.421
<font color="#fecb00">Rented a minivan.</font>

475
00:40:22.422 --> 00:40:25.801
<font color="#fecb00">That's good.
But I mean. how did you find me?</font>

476
00:40:26.635 --> 00:40:27.635
<font color="#fecb00">My mom.</font>

477
00:40:27.636 --> 00:40:29.221
<font color="#fecb00">- Emiko.
- Yes.</font>

478
00:40:33.976 --> 00:40:35.560
<font color="#fecb00">We found something in my father's safe.</font>

479
00:40:35.561 --> 00:40:37.270
<font color="#fecb00">- Kentaro.
- What? He's my great uncle Lee.</font>

480
00:40:37.271 --> 00:40:39.313
<font color="#fecb00">What did you find in the safe?</font>

481
00:40:39.314 --> 00:40:40.690
<font color="#fecb00">Old computer files.</font>

482
00:40:40.691 --> 00:40:43.235
<font color="#fecb00">Bunch of crazy shit. Monster shit.</font>

483
00:40:43.735 --> 00:40:47.364
<font color="#fecb00">Can you please.
please keep your voices down?</font>

484
00:40:48.657 --> 00:40:51.909
<font color="#fecb00">What's this all about? Why are you here?
And you gotta make it kinda quick.</font>

485
00:40:51.910 --> 00:40:54.079
<font color="#fecb00">We wanna find out
what happened to my father.</font>

486
00:40:55.205 --> 00:40:56.206
<font color="#fecb00">You tell me.</font>

487
00:40:57.499 --> 00:41:00.376
<font color="#fecb00">Right after G-Day.
he said he had someplace he needed to go.</font>

488
00:41:00.377 --> 00:41:01.544
<font color="#fecb00">Wouldn't tell us where.</font>

489
00:41:01.545 --> 00:41:03.462
<font color="#fecb00">but a week later
we were told the plane he was on</font>

490
00:41:03.463 --> 00:41:04.743
<font color="#fecb00">disappeared somewhere in Alaska.</font>

491
00:41:05.632 --> 00:41:07.843
<font color="#fecb00">Turns out he had
a whole secret life in Japan.</font>

492
00:41:08.886 --> 00:41:10.469
<font color="#fecb00">I came here to try and figure it out.</font>

493
00:41:10.470 --> 00:41:12.972
<font color="#fecb00">but now we're being chased by
these Monarch people and--</font>

494
00:41:12.973 --> 00:41:15.933
<font color="#fecb00">"Disappeared"? As in. no body?</font>

495
00:41:15.934 --> 00:41:17.519
<font color="#fecb00"><i>No death certificate?</i></font>

496
00:41:18.395 --> 00:41:20.522
<font color="#fecb00">- What are you saying?
- Hey.</font>

497
00:41:21.190 --> 00:41:22.566
<font color="#fecb00">Hey. what is this place?</font>

498
00:41:23.817 --> 00:41:28.779
<font color="#fecb00">This place is what Monarch
euphemistically refers to</font>

499
00:41:28.780 --> 00:41:30.824
<font color="#fecb00">as "secure asset management."</font>

500
00:41:32.075 --> 00:41:33.534
<font color="#fecb00">Right. So. you're imprisoned here.</font>

501
00:41:33.535 --> 00:41:35.369
<font color="#fecb00">Okay. Well. we're leaving.</font>

502
00:41:35.370 --> 00:41:37.872
<font color="#fecb00">Yeah. you can try.
but they're just gonna keep following you</font>

503
00:41:37.873 --> 00:41:41.460
<font color="#fecb00">and following you and following you.
until they finally get what they want.</font>

504
00:41:41.960 --> 00:41:42.960
<font color="#fecb00">Or?</font>

505
00:41:42.961 --> 00:41:44.338
<font color="#fecb00">Well. that's up to you.</font>

506
00:41:44.922 --> 00:41:47.340
<font color="#fecb00">Now. you can choke down
that mountain of Monarch bullshit</font>

507
00:41:47.341 --> 00:41:49.843
<font color="#fecb00">about your father disappearing
without a trace.</font>

508
00:41:53.472 --> 00:41:56.557
<font color="#fecb00">Or we can
get the hell outta here right now</font>

509
00:41:56.558 --> 00:41:58.894
<font color="#fecb00">and find out what really happened
