511
00:42:10.906 --> 00:42:12.115
<font color="#fecb00">What's it gonna be?</font>

512
00:42:19.623 --> 00:42:20.665
<font color="#fecb00">Here. this way.</font>

513
00:42:20.666 --> 00:42:21.999
<font color="#fecb00">Are you sure?</font>

514
00:42:22.000 --> 00:42:23.961
<font color="#fecb00">I did two tours in this tin can. Doc.</font>

515
00:42:28.507 --> 00:42:29.591
<font color="#fecb00">What is that?</font>

516
00:42:33.637 --> 00:42:36.306
<font color="#fecb00">- Let's keep it moving. Come on.
- Okay.</font>

517
00:42:40.727 --> 00:42:42.895
<font color="#fecb00">- Are you all right?
- Oh. Jesus Christ.</font>

518
00:42:42.896 --> 00:42:44.940
<font color="#fecb00">- Go back! Go!
- Oh. my God.</font>

519
00:42:49.069 --> 00:42:50.946
<font color="#fecb00">- Oh. my God!
- No.</font>

520
00:42:52.281 --> 00:42:53.407
<font color="#fecb00">Hang on!</font>

521
00:42:56.493 --> 00:42:58.328
<font color="#fecb00">It's leaving! Now's our chance!</font>

522
00:43:00.914 --> 00:43:02.290
<font color="#fecb00">- Push!
- I am pushing!</font>

523
00:43:02.291 --> 00:43:03.375
<font color="#fecb00">Come on!</font>

524
00:43:04.543 --> 00:43:05.543
<font color="#fecb00">Where'd it go?</font>

525
00:43:08.922 --> 00:43:10.173
<font color="#fecb00">Help!</font>

526
00:43:10.174 --> 00:43:11.257
<font color="#fecb00">Hurry!</font>

527
00:43:11.258 --> 00:43:12.967
<font color="#fecb00">What the hell is going on?</font>

528
00:43:12.968 --> 00:43:15.387
<font color="#fecb00">- Help! Help!
- Come on!</font>

529
00:43:16.180 --> 00:43:18.056
<font color="#fecb00">- Watch out!
- Holy shit!</font>

530
00:43:22.394 --> 00:43:24.937
<font color="#fecb00">Oh. my God!</font>

531
00:43:24.938 --> 00:43:26.106
<font color="#fecb00">Help me get him out!</font>

532
00:43:26.773 --> 00:43:28.482
<font color="#fecb00">Come on! Before it comes back!</font>

533
00:43:28.483 --> 00:43:29.568
<font color="#fecb00">Okay.</font>

534
00:43:30.110 --> 00:43:31.194
<font color="#fecb00">Here we go.</font>

535
00:43:31.195 --> 00:43:32.487
<font color="#fecb00">One. two. three.</font>

536
00:43:35.199 --> 00:43:36.200
<font color="#fecb00">It's too heavy.</font>

537
00:43:37.576 --> 00:43:40.077
<font color="#fecb00">I'm gonna stick this under.
