538
00:43:40.078 --> 00:43:41.078
<font color="#fecb00">Okay.</font>

539
00:43:41.079 --> 00:43:42.955
<font color="#fecb00">One. two. three.</font>

540
00:43:42.956 --> 00:43:48.836
<font color="#fecb00">Go! Get up! Billy! Hey. get up!</font>

541
00:43:48.837 --> 00:43:51.215
<font color="#fecb00">- Go!
- Okay.</font>

542
00:43:56.470 --> 00:43:57.470
<font color="#fecb00">Go!</font>

543
00:43:59.389 --> 00:44:00.849
<font color="#fecb00">Go. go. go!</font>

544
00:44:10.442 --> 00:44:11.944
<font color="#fecb00">Go!</font>

545
00:44:27.668 --> 00:44:28.919
<font color="#fecb00">Oh. my God.</font>

546
00:44:30.295 --> 00:44:31.338
<font color="#fecb00">It is a dragon.</font>

547
00:44:46.979 --> 00:44:50.023
